listings.comment: I recently worked with Ahmad A. on a website redesign, and I’m overall very happy with the outcome. Ahmad was professional, responsive, and patient throughout the process, happily accommodating as many edits as I needed along the way. While certain design aspects initially didn’t meet my expectations, Ahmad was receptive to feedback and worked diligently to make the necessary changes once I provided clear communication and detailed instructions. The final result is a site I’m proud of, and I’d definitely recommend Ahmad to others. I’d also be happy to work with him again in the future!

Ahmad is a pleasure to work with. He is courteous, professional and takes the time to make sure that all the details were right. After the job was finished he continued to check to make sure everything was working properly. We have used him in the past and will continue to do.

Ahmad A truly EXCELLED in delivering a high-quality WEBSITE DEVELOPMENT project. His attention to detail and thorough documentation went beyond my expectations, and his responsiveness and politeness made the process incredibly smooth. I couldn't have asked for a better experience! 👍

I like working Ahmad, because of his professionalism we are able to work through any problems, also he is very polite and will work very hard to make sure all timelines are met and honoured. It's a year later and I will continue to use him.  I will recommend him to anyone that needs his services.
Ahmad is a pleasure to work with. He went above and beyond to help us get our revisions up and running. He is courteous and professional. We will continue to use him
